<!DOCTYPE html>
  <html>

  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Restaurant Details</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <% include ../partials/siteNav.ejs %>

    <div class="container">
        <p class="h1 mt-4"><%= value[0].name%></p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-4">
                <% restId = value[0].restaurant_id; %>
                <% imgPath = "/Pictures/restaurant_" + restId + ".jpg" %>
                <img src="<%= imgPath %>" class="img-thumbnail" width="100%">
            </div>
            <div class="col-8">
                <p><%= value[0].description %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container mt-2">
            <%= dollars = "";%>
            <% if (value[0].price == 1) {dollars = "$";} else if (value[0].price == 2) {dollars = "$$";} else {dollars = "$$$"} %>
            <span class="badge badge-light"><%= dollars %></span>
            <span class="badge badge-light"><%= value[0].type %></span>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-6">
                <div class="mapouter">
                    <div class="gmap_canvas">
                        <% mapPath = "https://maps.google.com/maps?q=" + value[0].address + "&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed" %>
                        <iframe width="550" height="500" id="gmap_canvas" src="<%= mapPath %>" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0">
                        </iframe>
                        <a href="https://www.yellowrocketagency.com/%22%3E"></a>
                    </div>
                    <style>.mapouter{position:relative;text-align:right;height:500px;width:550px;}.gmap_canvas {overflow:hidden;background:none!important;height:500px;width:550px;}</style>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4">
                <h2><u>Hours:</u></h2>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Sunday : <%= value[0].sunday %></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Monday - From XX:XX to XX:XX</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Tuesday - From XX:XX to XX:XX</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Wednesday - From XX:XX to XX:XX</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Thursday - From XX:XX to XX:XX</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Friday - From XX:XX to XX:XX</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Saturday - From XX:XX to XX:XX</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <p align="center" class="h5 m-auto"><u>Comments and Reviews</u></p>
        <br>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-3"><strong>User #1</strong></div>
            <div class="col-9">
                <p>Etiam urna erat, blandit vel vulputate eu, pellentesque at nulla. Nullam hendrerit eros lorem, at eleifend quam pellentesque non. Cras eu commodo dolor.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3"><strong>User #2</strong></div>
            <div class="col-9">
                <p>Ut suscipit nisl eget consequat interdum. Quisque venenatis vestibulum ligula, nec consectetur mi tempor at. Mauris volutpat condimentum malesuada.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-3"><strong>User #3</strong></div>
            <div class="col-9">
                <p>Sed magna lorem, venenatis vitae auctor tempus, tincidunt mattis velit. Donec aliquet, lectus nec sollicitudin interdum, nisl tellus rutrum justo, in luctus augue purus ac nulla.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <form id="comment-form">
            <div class="form-group">
                <textarea class="form-control" id="comment" placeholder="Thoughts?  Comments?  Put them here!" name="comment"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mx-auto">Submit</button>
        </form>

        <br>
    </div>

    <% include ../partials/siteFooter.ejs %>


  </body>

</html>
